<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178252>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Maxillary palpus. A, Keilbachia acamptochaeta sp. n. (paratype). B, K. flabellata sp. n. (holotype). C, K. gigas sp. n. (holotype). D, K. fasciata sp. n. (holotype). E, K. foveolata sp. n. (holotype). F, K. bicuspis sp. n. (holotype). G, K. rima sp. n. (holotype). H, K. filigera sp. n. (holotype). I, K. oligonema sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178252/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178256>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Eye bridge, frontal view (A), and part of hypopygium (B, D) and gonostylus (C, E), ventral view. A, B, C, Keilbachia acamptochaeta sp. n. (holotype). D, E, K. bicuspis sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178256/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178254>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Apical part of fore tibia, prolateral view. A, Keilbachia oligonema sp. n. (Burma). B, K. fasciata sp. n. (paratype). C, K. rima sp. n. (holotype). D, K. acamptochaeta sp. n. (paratype). E, K. flabellata sp. n. (holotype). F, K. foveolata sp. n. (holotype). G, K. filigera sp. n. (holotype). H, K. bicuspis sp. n. (holotype). I, K. gigas sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178254/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

